description: Sunny top floor, 2 bed 2 bath condo with soaring ceilings, perfect for a savvy investor or city residence. The upper unit is bright and airy with an open concept kitchen and living space featuring updated appliances, granite countertops and a gas fireplace. Directly off the living room is a beautiful uncovered deck perfect for indoor outdoor entertaining. The bedrooms are equal size and both fit queen size beds with deep built in closets. There are 2 separate bathrooms, one with an updated glass enclosed shower and other with a jacuzzi tub. Plus in unit laundry. An additional bonus is the large storage in the private basement, perfect for bikes, suitcases and golf clubs. See floor plan for additional details. On street parking. Moments away from bars, restaurants and T stops plus all the South Boston has to offer.
